          "gameSystem": "nightbane",
          "reference": "Dark Designs (WB6)",
          "pageNumber": 136
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Nightbane's skin is covered with tattoos. Unlike normal body decorations, however, these tattoos change and move! The changes may reflect the character's current state of mind (i.e., an angry Nightbane might suddenly display violent or threatening tattoos) or might be controlled directly by the character (50-50 chance or select one). In the first case, the Nightbane has no control over the tattoos; they react to his emotions and may start squirming at any given moment.",
