          "gameSystem": "nightbane",
          "reference": "Dark Designs (WB6)",
          "pageNumber": 136
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Nightbane's body is covered by 2D6x10 tiny mouths! The mouths can make gestures, stick out their tongues, whistle, hoot, growl or even scream in a hellish chorus. However, they cannot speak. The character can also grapple an enemy and let the tiny mouths bite him (this inflicts 1D4 damage per mouth; typically 1D6 mouths will bite at the same time).",
      "statModifiers": {
        "hf": {
          "dice": "1D4+2"
